{"tid":702527,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開記招普京來電 俄主帥急接聽","createTime":"2018-06-15T03:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T03:51:39.000Z","uid":148652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb260a5f1a543c948f648b4094ba44cb206cffa9","tid":702527,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jamjwsv2oQStmIfrMXVX.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-06-15/953c55d0-703f-11e8-8d49-1de305272caf_GettyImages-974401282-side.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fjamjwsv2oQStmIfrMXVX.A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-06-15%2F953c55d0-703f-11e8-8d49-1de305272caf_GettyImages-974401282-side.jpg&h=f4b53eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯教練查捷索夫在賽後記招期間，獲總統普京來電道賀，不得不中斷訪問接聽。<br />\n<br />\n主辦國俄羅斯周四在世界盃揭幕賽以5:0大勝沙特阿拉伯，全國上下興奮不已，連現場觀戰的總統普京也笑得見牙不見眼，畢竟沒有人預計俄羅斯能取得如此大捷。教練查捷索夫賽後出席記者會，期間更接到普京的祝賀來電。 查捷索夫在侃侃而談之際，<span style=\"color: red;\">一看電話馬上聽著手機離開座位，面容忽然認真起來</span>，由梅開二度的卓利舒夫回答記者提問。不久，查捷索夫回到座位說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">是我們國家領導人來電</span>，他要我向球員致謝，還鼓勵我們要保持這樣的好表現。」 難怪查捷索夫連記者會也不理，原來是普京來電，希望下次普京能計好時間打電話，不然就會影響全球記者會的舉行。抑或，普京是故意博宣傳？真是天曉得了。<br />\n<br />\n-----------<br />\n<br />\n屌你笑左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea63bdd988653714cac4eb3af584fb1063b1f63f","tid":702527,"uid":53666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"唔講以為列寧打嚟"},{"pid":"6f3e1bb15f2c3bdfab1d3c3ca83a48b8ccecfdf6","tid":702527,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"唔聽電話 塭kgb 招呼"},{"pid":"4cfdc9133ff6b0eb36c5bf9cd4c0bde19e36cb32","tid":702527,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"輸左會點"}]}